## 12. API & EXTERNAL DEPENDENCIES

### 12.1 GitHub API Integration

**Endpoints**:
```typescript
// Repository metadata
GET https://api.github.com/repos/{owner}/{repo}

// File tree (recursive)
GET https://api.github.com/repos/{owner}/{repo}/git/trees/{sha}?recursive=1

// File content
GET https://api.github.com/repos/{owner}/{repo}/contents/{path}
```

**Rate Limiting**:
- Unauthenticated: 60 requests/hour
- Authenticated: 5000 requests/hour
- Strategy: Implement caching, use authenticated requests

### 12.2 Environment Configuration

Create `.env.local`:
```bash
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxx  # Personal access token
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
```

