## 14. PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS

### 14.1 Optimization Strategies

1. **Lazy Loading**: Load file contents only when needed
2. **Caching**: Cache parsed repositories in localStorage
3. **Pagination**: Limit initial file tree depth
4. **Debouncing**: Debounce URL validation (500ms)
5. **Web Workers**: Parse large repositories in background thread

### 14.2 Performance Targets

| Metric | Target | Measurement |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| URL Validation | < 500ms | Time to validate GitHub URL |
| Metadata Fetch | < 2s | Time to fetch repository info |
| Parsing (small repo) | < 5s | < 100 files |
| Parsing (large repo) | < 15s | 100-1000 files |
| Canvas Render | < 1s | Time to render graph |
| Story Generation | < 3s | Time to generate walkthrough |

